pulltitle: Bug 1653169 - Use py2 for this old copy of repo
pullsbody: This is a stop-gap for [bug 1653169](https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1653169), working around the bustage of this old copy of the repo tool with python3. The followup will be to merge from upstream.
pull_repo_desc: git-repo with modifcation to fix private repo access
pull_commit_message: Use py2 for this old copy of repo

pullsbody:
example of why this is needed: https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/tinderbox-builds/mozilla-release-macosx64/release-mozilla-release-firefox-linux64_partner_repacks-bm84-build1-build23.txt.gz
